title: Canterbury, Leo, Heritage & Blackhawk Christian advance to boys soccer regional final
text:
Canterbury, Leo, Heritage & Blackhawk Christian advance to boys soccer regional final 
By Eric Dutkiewicz - 21Alive October 16, 2015 Updated Oct 16, 2015 at 11:14 AM EDT 
IHSAA Boys Soccer State Tournament Class 2A Semi-Final : Leo 2, South Side 0 F 
Semi-Final : Canterbury 3, Homestead 0 F 
Championship : Leo at Canterbury, 6pm Saturday 
Class 1A 
Semi-Final : Heritage 2, Lakewood Park Christian 1 F 
Semi-Final : Blackhawk Christian 1, Westview 0 F 
Championship : Heritage at Blackhawk Christian, 7pm Saturday
